      "description": "Four-loop HQET integral topology 5 for the matter-dependent cusp anomalous dimension at small angle. Defined via 16 propagators $D_k$ with $G(a_1,...,a_{16}) = e^{4 \\varepsilon \\gamma_E} \\int \\prod D_k^{-a_k}$, restricting $a_1=a_3=0$ and $a_4,a_5,a_{10},a_{11} \\geq 0$. Contains 3 HQET (Wilson line) propagators linear in $v.k_i$ combinations and 7 standard massless quadratic propagators. Two of the three new master integrals belong to this topology. Computed via Feynman parametrization and HyperInt, checked with FIESTA4. Topologies 1-3 are defined in the companion paper arXiv:1708.01221.",
